SSAW (Support Survivors of African War) is an NGO
dedicated to providing aid to communities affected by war,
natural disasters, and climate change worldwide. Our focus
includes supporting refugees, offering essential
humanitarian aid such as food, clothing, medical supplies,
and clean water, as well as rebuilding schools and providing
psychological support. Initially concentrating on Africa and
Mediterranean routes to Italy, SSAW aims to create long-
term positive impacts by improving lives and restoring hope.
We seek to build effective partnerships for comprehensive
support and sustainable community recovery.
